{"title":"山中打靶","authors":["徐国志"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":2,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山中打靶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重庆兴华机器厂工人　徐国志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厚厚的云层压在山顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急雨狂风横扫森林。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨中民兵打靶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团队的旗帜火一样鲜明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耳听一声“卧倒”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是指挥员发出的号令。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥泞、荆棘压在身下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密集的雨帘遮不住明亮的眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手托着三八式步枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸腔里热血沸腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老八路用过的枪呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传给了我们这代年青人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨亮的枪柄上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留着前辈的指纹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级的仇、阶级的恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝进这小小的准星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕它雨密风紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先辈的话儿记得清："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱要紧握手中的枪啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练出过硬的本领。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“啪！啪！啪！”子弹出膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山谷里响起强大的回声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵靶旗飞舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨中飘起朵朵红云。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}